    • Enum Constant Detail

      • VENDOR

        public static final Intention.Field VENDOR
        Vendor which generated this intent. This is applicable for all intents and is always present. Its value is array with one string. e.g. "vendor":["HERE"]

      • VERSION

        public static final Intention.Field VERSION
        Version of the deduced intention. This is applicable for all intents and is always present.Its value is an array with one string in the format of major.minor.build. e.g. "version":["1.0.2"]

      • LANGUAGE

        public static final Intention.Field LANGUAGE
        Language used for deduction. This is applicable for all intents and is always present. Its value is an array that contains one of the following:
        • Intention.Value.ENGLISH

        e.g. "language":["eng"]

      • DOMAIN

        public static final Intention.Field DOMAIN
        Knowledge domain. e.g. "domain":["map.routing"]. This is not currently returned in any intent.

      • DURATION

        public static final Intention.Field DURATION
        Request processing time for your information only. This is applicable for all intents and is always present. e.g. "duration":["0ms"]

      • FUNCTION

        public static final Intention.Field FUNCTION
        Function of the intent. This is applicable for all intents and is always present. Its value is an array that contains at least one of the values defined in Intention.Function. e.g. "func":["ROUTE_FROM_TO"] e.g. "func":["START_TALKING","DISTANCE_FROM_TO"]

      • TEXT

        public static final Intention.Field TEXT
        Sentence that produced this intention. This is applicable for all intents and is always present. Its value a array of one string. e.g. "text":["where am i"]

      • OPTIMIZE

        public static final Intention.Field OPTIMIZE
        Optimize the route by reordering stops on the route for the following intents and may not always be present:
        • Intention.Function.ADD_STOPOVER
        • Intention.Function.ROUTE_FROM_TO

        Its values is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.TRUE
        • Intention.Value.FALSE

        e.g. "optimize":["false_"]

      • REROUTE

        public static final Intention.Field REROUTE
        Determines whether an alternative route should be requested in in Intention.Function.ROUTE_FROM_TO intent and may not always be present. Its value is an array that contains one of the following values:
        • Intention.Value.ON
        • Intention.Value.OFF

        e.g. "reroute":["on_"]

        Note that REROUTE means to stop using the existing route and get a new route to the same destination. On the other hand, ALTERNATIVE_ROUTE means to stop using the existing route and get a new route to an alternative destination.

      • ARRIVAL_TIME

        public static final Intention.Field ARRIVAL_TIME
        Arrival time for the following intents and may not always be present:
        • Intention.Function.TIME_FROM_TO
        • Intention.Function.POI

        Its value is an array that contains one string.

        e.g. "I have to be in seattle by 5" --> "arrival_time":["5"]

        e.g. "I have to be in seattle by 5pm" --> "arrival_time":["5pm"]

        This is the concatenation of the values for ARRIVAL_TIME_VALUE and TIME_SUFFIX if TIME_SUFFIX exists.

      • ARRIVAL_TIME_VALUE

        public static final Intention.Field ARRIVAL_TIME_VALUE
        Arrival time value for the following intents and may not always be present:
        • Intention.Function.TIME_FROM_TO
        • Intention.Function.POI

        Its value is an array that contains one string that represents the arrival time without am/pm suffix.

        e.g. "I have to be in seattle by 5" --> "arrival_time_value":["5"]

        e.g. "I have to be in seattle by 5pm" --> "arrival_time_value":["5"]

      • TIME_SUFFIX

        public static final Intention.Field TIME_SUFFIX
        AM/PM time suffix for the following intents and may not always be present:
        • Intention.Function.TIME_FROM_TO
        • Intention.Function.POI

        Its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.AM
        • Intention.Value.PM

        e.g. "I have to be in seattle by 5" --> not present

        e.g. "I have to be in seattle by 5pm" --> "time_suffix":["pm"]

        • Intention.Value.HOURS

        • Intention.Value.EVENT_HEALTH

      • FROM

        public static final Intention.Field FROM
        Used to indicate the source for the intent. For the following intents, it may not always be present:
        • Intention.Function.ROUTE_FROM_TO
        • Intention.Function.DISTANCE_FROM_TO
        • Intention.Function.TIME_FROM_TO

        Its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • a string indicating a location
        • Intention.Value.COLLECTION_OBJ

        For the following intents, it's always present:

        • Intention.Function.COPY_COLLECTION
        • Intention.Function.RENAME_COLLECTION

        Its value is an array that contains one string.

        For Intention.Function.POI intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains Intention.Value.COLLECTION_OBJ.

      • TARGET

        public static final Intention.Field TARGET
        Use to indicate the target for the intent.

        For Intention.Function.CALL_NUMBER intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.HOME
        • Intention.Value.WORK
        • a string that represents a contact name
        • a string that contains a phone number
        • a string that represents a search category

        For Intention.Function.CHANGE_MAP_CENTER intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.ORIGIN
        • a string that indicates a location

        For Intention.Function.CHECK_COLLECTION intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.HOME
        • Intention.Value.WORK
        • a string that indicates a location

        For the following intents, it's always present:

        • Intention.Function.COPY_COLLECTION
        • Intention.Function.RENAME_COLLECTION

        Its value is an array that contains one string representing the target collection.

        For Intention.Function.DOWNLOAD intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains one string that indicates a location.

        For Intention.Function.REMOVE intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.IT_OR_THERE
        • Intention.Value.DESTINATION_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.STOPOVER_OBJ
        • a string that represents the item to be removed

        For Intention.Function.REMOVE_FROM_CONTACTS intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains a string representing the contact to be removed.

        For Intention.Function.REMOVE_FROM_MAP, it's always present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.ALL_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.ROUTE_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.STOPOVER_OBJ
        • a string that presents the ordinal of the objects on the map
        • a string that presents a category of the objects on the map
        • a string that presents the object on the map

        For Intention.Function.SEND_MESSAGE intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.MYSELF
        • Intention.Value.FACEBOOK
        • Intention.Value.TWITTER
        • a string that reprents a contact name

        For Intention.Function.TALK_SPEED intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.LESS
        • Intention.Value.MORE
        • Intention.Value.NORMAL
        • Intention.Value.MINIMUM
        • Intention.Value.MAXIMUM

        For Intention.Function.VOLUME intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.LESS
        • Intention.Value.MORE
        • Intention.Value.MINIMUM
        • Intention.Value.MAXIMUM
        • a number string that represents a percentage, e.g. 50 for 50%.

        For Intention.Function.WEB_SEARCH intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains a search topic.

        For Intention.Function.ZOOM intent, it's always present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.LESS
        • Intention.Value.MORE

        For Intention.Function.ADD_STOPOVER intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains a string that indicates a category for the search.

        For Intention.Function.ADDRESS intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.DESTINATION_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.NEXT_MANEUVER_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.STOPOVER_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.HOME
        • Intention.Value.WORK

        For Intention.Function.ELEVATION intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.HOME
        • Intention.Value.WORK
        • a string that indicates a location

        For Intention.Function.COLLECT_LOCATION intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains one of the following value:

        • Intention.Value.HOME
        • Intention.Value.WORK
        • Intention.Value.CAR
        • a string that indicates the name for the location to be collected.

        For Intention.Function.POI intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • a string that indicates a category for the search, e.g. restaurant.
        • a string that indicates a place name, e.g. starbucks.
        • a string that indicates an address.
        • Intention.Value.COLLECTION_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.IT_OR_THERE

        For the following intents, it may not always be present:

        • Intention.Function.DISTANCE_FROM_TO
        • Intention.Function.PLACE_INFO
        • Intention.Function.ROUTE_FROM_TO
        • Intention.Function.TIME_FROM_TO

        Its value is an array that contains one of the folliwing value:

        • Intention.Value.DESTINATION_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.STOPOVER_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.NEXT_MANEUVER_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.ORIGIN
        • Intention.Value.IT_OR_THERE
        • Intention.Value.HOME
        • Intention.Value.WORK
        • a string that indicates a category, e.g. restaurant.
        • a string that indicates a place name, e.g. starbucks.
        • a string that indicates an address.

        For the following intents, it may not always be present:

        • Intention.Function.REMOVE_FROM_COLLECTION
        • Intention.Function.REMOVE_FROM_ROUTE

        Its value is an array that contains on of the following:

        • Intention.Value.ALL_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.IT_OR_THERE
        • a string that indicates the ordinal of the object to be removed.
        • a string that indicates a category of objects to be removed.
        • a string that indicates the object to be removed.

        For Intention.Function.REPORT_GEO_EVENT intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains one string that presents the event, e.g. crime, hear attack, road accident, ...etc.

        For Intention.Function.SAVE_PHONE_NUMBER intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains a phone number string.

        For Intention.Function.SEND_LOCATION intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.MYSELF
        • Intention.Value.FACEBOOK
        • Intention.Value.TWITTER
        • a string that reprents a contact name
        • a string that contains a phone number

        For Intention.Function.SYS_TIME intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.ORIGIN
        • Intention.Value.IT_OR_THERE
        • Intention.Value.HOME
        • Intention.Value.WORK
        • a string that indicates a location

        For Intention.Function.TRAFFIC intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.ROUTE_OBJ
        • Intention.Value.ORIGIN
        • Intention.Value.IT_OR_THERE
        • Intention.Value.HOME
        • Intention.Value.WORK
        • a string that indicates a location

        For the following intents, it may not always be present:

        • Intention.Function.USE_FIRST
        • Intention.Function.USE_LAST
        • Intention.Function.USE_NEXT
        • Intention.Function.USE_PREV

        Its value is an array that contains one of the following:

        • Intention.Value.ROUTE_OBJ
        • a string that indicates a search topic

        For Intention.Function.USE_LANGUAGE intent, it may not always be present and its value is an array that contains one of the following string:

        • Intention.Value.NONE
        • Intention.Value.ENGLISH
        • Intention.Value.FRENCH
        • Intention.Value.GERMAN

      • ALTERNATIVE_ROUTE

        public static final Intention.Field ALTERNATIVE_ROUTE
        Indicates whether to calculate a route for Intention.Function.ROUTE_FROM_TO intent and may not always be present. Its value is an array that contains one of the following:
        • Intention.Value.TRUE
        • Intention.Value.FALSE

        When absent, it should be assumed to be Intention.Value.FALSE.

        Note that ALTERNATIVE_ROUTE means to stop using the existing route and get a new route to an alternative destination. E.g. instead of the current route to the closest Startbucks, show route to a different Startbucks. On the other hand, REROUTE means to stop using the existing route and get a new route to the same destination.
